name: Pages-test
body:
### Testing the **Pages** feature of GitHub.

If this works it will be pretty cool, especially when using custom domains. Mostly because:

- I have a bunch of domains just lying around.
- I'd like to do something with them.
  - I don't want to pay to host the silly things I do with them.

*This Page* also functions as some further practice of Markdown. 

----

I think I like Markdown.
